<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="22" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1436,796,1216]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,267,1084,1109]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Remarks.</emphasis>
Both the structure of valves and the morphology of the girdle elements suggest that 
<taxonomicName box="[1264,1435,1084,1109]" class="Polyplacophora" family="Chitonidae" genus="Chiton" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neoloricata" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="furtivus">
<emphasis box="[1264,1435,1084,1109]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Chiton furtivus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
belongs to the genus 
<taxonomicName authority="J. E. Gray, 1821" authorityName="J.E. Gray" authorityYear="1821" box="[396,744,1119,1144]" class="Polyplacophora" family="Ischnochitonidae" genus="Lepidochitona" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neoloricata" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Mollusca" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[396,558,1119,1144]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Lepidochitona</emphasis>
J.E. Gray, 1821
</taxonomicName>
(Kaas &amp; van 
<bibRefCitation box="[908,1043,1119,1144]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refId="ref85410" refString="Kaas, P. &amp; van Belle, R. A. (1981) The genus Lepidochitona Gray, 1821 in the Northeastern Atlantic Ocean, the Mediterranean Sea and the Black Sea. Zoologische Verhandelingen, 185, 1 - 43." type="journal article">Belle, 1981</bibRefCitation>
: 37). Gaglini (in Settepassi, 1985) designated and figured the 
<typeStatus box="[464,571,1156,1181]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">lectotype</typeStatus>
. Recorded by MolluscaBase (2018) as 
<taxonomicName authority="(Monterosato, 1879)" authorityName="Monterosato" authorityYear="1879" baseAuthorityName="Monterosato" baseAuthorityYear="1879" class="Polyplacophora" family="Ischnochitonidae" genus="Lepidochitona" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neoloricata" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="furtiva">
<emphasis box="[1022,1269,1156,1181]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Lepidochitona furtiva</emphasis>
(Monterosato, 1879)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
